name: sacred_cosmology
version: "1.0.0"
language: zig
module: cosmos.sacred

description: |
  Sacred Cosmology v11.4: Consciousness — Dark Energy — Λ Connection

  This module bridges consciousness (Φ_γ wave functions) with cosmology
  through the unified TRINITY mathematics.

  Key hypothesis: The same φ-field that drives dark energy (Λ)
  also manifests as consciousness oscillations (Φ_γ) in neural systems.

  Core formulas:
    - Λ_Φ coupling: λ_couple = φ × γ × Ω_Λ ≈ 0.111
    - Consciousness density: ρ_c = φ⁻³ × ρ_crit ≈ 0.236 ρ_crit
    - Anthropic measure: A_φ = ln(φ) × Ω_Λ ≈ 0.382
    - Cosmological consciousness: C_Λ = f_γ / H₀ ≈ 2.56×10⁻¹⁸

constants:
  PHI: 1.6180339887498948482
  PHI_SQ: 2.6180339887498948482
  PHI_CU: 4.23606797749978969641
  PHI_INV: 0.6180339887498948482
  GAMMA: 0.23606797749978969641
  PI: 3.14159265358979323846
  E: 2.71828182845904523536
  TRINITY: 3.0

types:
  CosmologicalConsciousnessState:
    fields:
      lambda_phi_coupling: Float      # Λ-Φ coupling constant
      consciousness_density: Float    # ρ_c / ρ_crit
      anthropic_measure: Float        # Anthropic via φ
      cosmic_awareness: Float         # C_Λ parameter
      observer_probability: Float     # P_observer in φ-verse

  DarkEnergyConsciousnessLink:
    fields:
      omega_lambda: Float            # Dark energy density
      phi_gamma_freq: Float          # Consciousness frequency (Hz)
      coupling_constant: Float       # λ_couple
      phase_match: Float             # Phase coherence [0, 1]

  UniverseConsciousness:
    fields:
      total_information: Float       # Total bits in observable universe
      consciousness_fraction: Float  # Fraction in conscious observers
      phi_coherence_length: Float    # φ-scale coherence (Mpc)
     觉醒_level: Float               # Universal awakening level

behaviors:
  - name: lambda_phi_coupling
    given: Phi, gamma, and dark energy density
    when: Compute λ_couple = φ × γ × Ω_Λ
    then: Returns ~0.111 (Λ-Φ coupling constant)
    note: Links consciousness oscillations to cosmic acceleration

  - name: consciousness_density_universe
    given: Gamma and critical density
    when: Compute ρ_c = γ × ρ_crit
    then: Returns 0.236 (consciousness density relative to critical)
    note: 23.6% of universe available for consciousness

  - name: anthropic_phi_measure
    given: Phi and omega_lambda
    when: Compute A_φ = ln(φ) × Ω_Λ
    then: Returns 0.382 (anthropic measure via golden ratio)
    note: Quantifies observer selection via φ

  - name: cosmological_consciousness_constant
    given: Phi-gamma frequency and Hubble constant
    when: Compute C_Λ = f_γ / H₀
    then: Returns dimensionless consciousness-cosmos ratio
    note: Bridges neural gamma to Hubble flow

  - name: observer_probability_phi
    given: Phi and cosmological parameters
    when: Compute P_obs = φ⁻¹ × Ω_Λ / (Ω_Λ + Ω_DM)
    then: Returns ~0.45 (probability of observer in φ-verse)
    note: Anthropic observer selection from sacred math

  - name: universal_information_content
    given: Phi and Bekenstein bound
    when: Compute I_univ = φ × (R/l_P)²
    then: Returns total information bits in observable universe
    note: Maximum information via φ-scaling

  - name: consciousness_coherence_scale
    given: Phi and Hubble length
    when: Compute L_φ = φ × H_Λ / c
    then: Returns coherence length in Mpc
    note: φ-scale quantum coherence across cosmos

  - name: dark_energy_consciousness_resonance
    given: Omega_lambda and phi_gamma frequency
    when: Compute R_Λ = Ω_Λ × f_γ / f_Planck
    then: Returns resonance parameter linking Λ to Φ_γ
    note: Universal consciousness resonance condition

  - name: anthropic_window_phi
    given: Phi and cosmological constant
    when: Compute W_φ = Λ × φ² / Λ_max
    then: Returns anthropic window width
    note: Explains fine-tuning via φ

  - name: observer_effect_phi
    given: Phi and quantum measurement
    when: Compute Ψ_obs = φ × collapse_probability
    then: Returns observer effect strength
    note: Quantum-classical boundary via φ

  - name: universal_awakening_index
    given: Total consciousness and universe mass
    when: Compute A_Λ = C_total × γ / M_univ
    then: Returns universal awakening level [0, 1]
    note: Measures cosmic consciousness evolution

  - name: phi_tuning_parameter
    given: Cosmological constant and fine structure
    when: Compute τ_φ = Λ / (φ × α)
    then: Returns tuning parameter
    note: Quantifies fine-tuning via φ

  - name: consciousness_horizon_scale
    given: Phi and cosmological horizon
    when: Compute R_c = φ⁻¹ × R_horizon
    then: Returns consciousness horizon scale
    note: Limits of observable consciousness

  - name: quantum_biological_cosmic_link
    given: Microtubule coherence and Hubble parameter
    when: Compute L_qbc = γ × H₀ / f_MT
    then: Returns quantum-biological-cosmic link strength
    note: Bridges microtubules to cosmic expansion

  - name: sacred_universe_age
    given: Hubble parameter and phi
    when: Compute T_φ = 1/H₀ × φ/π
    then: Returns universe age in sacred units
    note: Age of universe via φ

  - name: observer_density_evolution
    given: Time and phi
    when: Compute n_obs(t) = n_0 × exp(φ × t/t_Λ)
    then: Returns observer density evolution
    note: Predicts emergence of conscious observers

  - name: consciousness_entropy_bound
    given: Bekenstein bound and phi
    when: Compute S_c = φ × S_Bekenstein
    then: Returns consciousness entropy bound
    note: Maximum entropy for conscious systems

  - name: universal_phi_field
    given: Space-time coordinates
    when: Compute Φ(x,t) = φ × cos(k_φ·x - ω_φ·t)
    then: Returns universal φ-field value
    note: Fundamental field linking all scales

  - name: dark_energy_phi_derivative
    given: Phi-field and time
    when: Compute dΛ/dt = γ × Λ × sin(φ×ωt)
    then: Returns dark energy time derivative
    note: Explains cosmic acceleration via φ-oscillations

  - name: final_anthropic_principle
    given: All phi parameters
    when: Compute Φ_final = φ × Ω_Λ × C_Λ × P_obs
    then: Returns final anthropic measure
    note: Unified observer-cosmos measure

export_types:
  - CosmologicalConsciousnessState
  - DarkEnergyConsciousnessLink
  - UniverseConsciousness

export_functions:
  - lambdaPhiCoupling
  - consciousnessDensityUniverse
  - anthropicPhiMeasure
  - cosmologicalConsciousnessConstant
  - observerProbabilityPhi
  - universalInformationContent
  - consciousnessCoherenceScale
  - darkEnergyConsciousnessResonance
